imdb.plot outline: WAG NATION follows the lives of five wives and girlfriends of some of Australia's most famous sporting stars. The show takes you through the highs and lows of supporting a professional sporting career while managing the daily pressures of having a relationship spread across the tabloids. The cast includes Terry Biviano, NRL WAG of Anthony Minichiello, Lynette Bolton, AFL WAG of Jude Bolton, Jana Peterson, NRL WAG of Matthew See, Jackie Spong, AFL WAG of Jarred Waite, and Chantelle Raleigh, NBL WAG of Adam Gibson. The 10-part series is a voyeuristic look into the lives of these five glamorous women as they juggle life and love with a fast-paced social calendar packed with launch events, fund-raising galas, movie premieres and front row seats at Fashion Week.
